---
layout: base.njk
locale: es
title: Libros
description: Un estante de libros construido con mis fuentes de Coleccion de Palabras.
permalink: /es/books/
---

<style>
  .books-intro {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .books-stats {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    border: 2px solid var(--clr-border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--clr-main-bg) 88%, var(--clr-nav-bg) 12%);
  }

  .books-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .book-card {
    border: 2px solid var(--clr-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--clr-main-bg);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 color-mix(in srgb, var(--clr-text) 45%, transparent);
  }

  .book-cover-wrap {
    aspect-ratio: 2 / 3;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--clr-main-bg) 70%, var(--clr-nav-bg) 30%), var(--clr-main-bg)),
      repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) 0 10px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 10px 20px);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--clr-border);
    position: relative;
  }

  .book-cover {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: none;
  }

  .book-cover-placeholder {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 14px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .book-content {
    padding: 12px;
  }

  .book-title {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--clr-heading);
  }

  .book-author {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    opacity: 0.88;
  }

  .book-meta {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 6px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .book-source {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    opacity: 0.75;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--clr-border-dashed);
    padding-top: 8px;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .books-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<h1>Libros</h1>
<p class="books-intro">
  Un estante practico creado con tus fuentes de <strong>Books/Novels</strong> dentro de Coleccion de Palabras.
  Las portadas se consultan en Open Library cuando estan disponibles.
</p>
<div class="books-stats">
  <strong>{{ booksPage.totalBooks }}</strong>
  <span>libros registrados</span>
</div>

{% if booksPage.books.length %}
  <section class="books-grid" aria-label="Lista de libros">
    {% for book in booksPage.books %}
      <article class="book-card">
        <div class="book-cover-wrap">
          {% if book.coverPath %}
            <img
              class="book-cover"
              src="{{ book.coverPath }}"
              alt="Portada de {{ book.title }}"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              style="display: block;"
            />
          {% else %}
            <div class="book-cover-placeholder">Portada no disponible</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="book-content">
          <h2 class="book-title">{{ book.title }}</h2>
          {% if book.author %}
            <p class="book-author">de {{ book.author }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="book-meta">
            <div>{{ book.wordsCount }} palabra{% if book.wordsCount != 1 %}s{% endif %} curada{% if book.wordsCount != 1 %}s{% endif %} de esta fuente</div>
            {% if book.firstSeen %}
              <div>Primera vez: {{ book.firstSeen | formatDate('es-MX') }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if book.lastSeen %}
              <div>Ultima vez: {{ book.lastSeen | formatDate('es-MX') }}</div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="book-source">Fuente: {{ book.source }}</div>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
{% else %}
  <p>Aun no se encontraron libros en Books/Novels.</p>
{% endif %}
